<plot>John Durham is a man without hope. A small-town factory worker working, sleeping, drinking his life away, Durham has long since given up on finding happiness or escaping from his lonely world. When he meets Mary, a high school girl full of dreams and future, John finds himself believing again, falling in love, and realizing in the process the redemption and pain that hope brings.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?341407</url></doc>
